                <img src="~/Areas/Topic/Sources/20170106/images/centent_3_main_bg.png">
                <div class="centent_3_main">
                    <div class="centent_3_main_top">
                        <div class="centent_3_main_top_left">
                            <img src="~/Areas/Topic/Sources/20170106/images/centent_3_main_top_left_img.png">
                            <p><b>活动期间：</b>邀请的好友（被邀请人）投资（可以<br />是邀请的多个好友累加的投资额）≥200万，即奖<br />励邀请人iPhone7 plus 128G玫瑰金 标配一部；</p>
                        </div>
